ch.nolix.common.container

Interface IContainer<E>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Clearable, java.lang.Iterable<E>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    List, Matrix

    public interface IContainer<E>
extends java.lang.Iterable<E>, Clearable
    A container can store several elements of a certain type. The default methods of this interface need to be overwritten only when the overriding implementation may call the default implementation.
